front.title: Alert My Star Destroyer! (V)
front.gametext: Deploy on table. During your deploy phase, you may reveal one Star Destroyer from hand to take its matching pilot character (or vice versa) into hand from Reserve Deck, and deploy both simultaneously (for -1 Force each); reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: For important Imperial dignitaries, an individual Star Destroyer is placed at their disposal.
